{"tid":1980938,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"通訊局屈港台煽動仇恨 人權法制裁名單使唔使加主席譚允芝入去？","createTime":"2020-04-20T11:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T11:52:52.000Z","uid":101392,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"802d114d8a43cb4de23332779e65a2dd70279fe0","tid":1980938,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:31:50.000Z","msg":"通訊局主席：譚允芝（資深大律師）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.coms-auth.hk/mobile/tc/about_us/members/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coms-auth.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftc%2Fabout_us%2Fmembers%2Findex.html&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPvroWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=f24a9e9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.coms-auth.hk/mobile/tc/about_us/members/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n譚允芝威水史：<br />\n<br />\n1. 撐人大釋法<br />\n她批評青年新政梁頌恆和游蕙禎在立法會<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">宣誓時，不必要地踩到國家安全和領土完整的底線，行為「好小學雞」</span></span>。至於會否釋法會演變成干預本港法律，她稱現時言之尚早，要先看到釋法的條文，又稱若然令本港法律更清晰，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">釋法未必一定是不好的事</span></span><a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/批青政宣誓-好小學雞-踩國家底線-譚允芝-如令本港法律更清楚-釋法未必不好/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%89%B9%E9%9D%92%E6%94%BF%E5%AE%A3%E8%AA%93-%E5%A5%BD%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E9%9B%9E-%E8%B8%A9%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%95%E7%B7%9A-%E8%AD%9A%E5%85%81%E8%8A%9D-%E5%A6%82%E4%BB%A4%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E6%9B%B4%E6%B8%85%E6%A5%9A-%E9%87%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%AA%E5%BF%85%E4%B8%8D%E5%A5%BD%2F&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPvroWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=bc62cf88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%89%B9%E9%9D%92%E6%94%BF%E5%AE%A3%E8%AA%93-%E5%A5%BD%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E9%9B%9E-%E8%B8%A9%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%95%E7%B7%9A-%E8%AD%9A%E5%85%81%E8%8A%9D-%E5%A6%82%E4%BB%A4%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E6%9B%B4%E6%B8%85%E6%A5%9A-%E9%87%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%AA%E5%BF%85%E4%B8%8D%E5%A5%BD%2F&h=00f976c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/批青政宣誓-好小學雞-踩國家底線-譚允芝-如令本港法律更清楚-釋法未必不好/</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 撐網絡23條<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/撐-網絡23條-被指離地-大律師公會主席譚允芝-有咩人貼地得過我/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%92%90-%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A123%E6%A2%9D-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E9%9B%A2%E5%9C%B0-%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E8%AD%9A%E5%85%81%E8%8A%9D-%E6%9C%89%E5%92%A9%E4%BA%BA%E8%B2%BC%E5%9C%B0%E5%BE%97%E9%81%8E%E6%88%91%2F&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPvroWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=08cc7132\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%92%90-%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A123%E6%A2%9D-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E9%9B%A2%E5%9C%B0-%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E8%AD%9A%E5%85%81%E8%8A%9D-%E6%9C%89%E5%92%A9%E4%BA%BA%E8%B2%BC%E5%9C%B0%E5%BE%97%E9%81%8E%E6%88%91%2F&h=5ee2e50b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/撐-網絡23條-被指離地-大律師公會主席譚允芝-有咩人貼地得過我/</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 話學校掛政治橫額唔算學術討論，係「測試法律底線」<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=236208\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D236208&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPvroWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=e8d34c4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D236208&h=0b784766\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=236208</a><br />\n大律師公會前主席譚允芝指，《刑事罪行條例》是相當舊的條文，懸掛橫額有可能會觸犯，她認為不應該測試法律底線，因為所有自由和權利均有規範及界線。<br />\n<br />\n譚允芝又指，並非在大學的大閘內所有發生的事情都涉及學術討論，單純是張起橫額鼓吹某個政治立場不算是學術討論。<br />\n<br />\n4. 少數唔參與「反《逃犯條例》聯署」嘅大律師公會前主席：<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/逃犯條例-12-名前任現任大律師公會主席-遺憾政府硬推修例-政府指-法官把關-實屬誤導/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-12-%E5%90%8D%E5%89%8D%E4%BB%BB%E7%8F%BE%E4%BB%BB%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-%E9%81%BA%E6%86%BE%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%A1%AC%E6%8E%A8%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8C%87-%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E6%8A%8A%E9%97%9C-%E5%AF%A6%E5%B1%AC%E8%AA%A4%E5%B0%8E%2F&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPvroWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=10e3f8b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-12-%E5%90%8D%E5%89%8D%E4%BB%BB%E7%8F%BE%E4%BB%BB%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-%E9%81%BA%E6%86%BE%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%A1%AC%E6%8E%A8%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8C%87-%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E6%8A%8A%E9%97%9C-%E5%AF%A6%E5%B1%AC%E8%AA%A4%E5%B0%8E%2F&h=ebd94f01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/逃犯條例-12-名前任現任大律師公會主席-遺憾政府硬推修例-政府指-法官把關-實屬誤導/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5. 屈港台《左右紅藍綠》煽動仇恨，打壓市民言論自由、港台編採自主<br />\n<br />\n仲有幫鄭若驊僭建講好說話之類<br />\n各位巴絲搵到再加"},{"pid":"83ce10bc60c931b2bbd30d74b8fef6cf7e6f2ba1","tid":1980938,"uid":36073,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:32:40.000Z","msg":"絕對要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6885b313f49202aef29b84476812a33a8127751a","tid":1980938,"uid":78570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:41:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9415411177558d3ac2ca05dea7e0d9b42373d7c9","tid":1980938,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T11:42:08.000Z","msg":"一個都未郁到<br />\n加成堆marginal既人入去做乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca2f06c1d226daafdfb2806035038fd31c2267